More commonly known as Tower 8, this new generation office tower offers all the amenity and quality you would expect of a near new building. 

A rare opportunity now exists to sublease some 985sqm of high quality fully fitted office space. The space features meeting rooms, amazing breakout areas and a high quality, open plan workstation environment.  

Tower 8 is 100m west of the GPO nestled amongst the emerging office and laneway precincts. Public transport and car parking is readily accessible and there are many retail offerings in the vicinity.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: RARE LEASING OPPORTUNITY IN HIGH QUALITY CENTRAL CBD BUILDING

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Positioned in amongst the action on Halifax Street this location presents the ideal spot to run your business. It offers a prominent CBD frame location that takes advantage of being a stone’s throw from the heart of the CBD but out of the hustle and bustle the CBD core provides.

The front of the property is open plan with one glass partitioned office to the rear of the tenancy that then flows through to the back half of the property creating a ‘back of house’ feel that a business may require - this space can be opened up through double doors to create more of a flow on feel through the premises subject to the prospective tenants needs. 

For further information or to organise an inspection please contact us at any stage.

44 Waymouth Street is an exceptional opportunity in the popular Waymouth Street precinct. With a recent refurbishment program that included a new foyer and upgrades of the lift lobbies, toilets and lift cars, the accommodation is ideal for the small to medium business seeking well presented office space.

One whole floor is available to lease plus smaller tenancies from 93sqm to 285sqm available. With all areas considered, there are options of utilising existing fitouts or having the building owner assist the incoming tenant with the modification or construction of a new fitout to suit.

Located in the thriving Waymouth Street precinct adjacent Topham Mall. The Waymouth Street precinct has undergone a significant re-positioning in recent years with some of the best amenity in the city including well regarded restaurants and cafés such as Press, Melt, Proof, The Gallery, Georges and Rigonis which are all located within easy walking distance.
